name: 22 Naiad
description: Although the ability to control water is not an uncommon ability on ‘The inside’ when humans from the ‘The Other Side’ first encountered people with such a power, they were lost for words. The term Naiad became common use to describe these mystical beings, becoming increasingly popular when women and girls from ‘The inside’ who were fascinated with rituals and cultures of ‘The Other Side’ began taking part in their ceremonies of worship. This practice was eventually stopped when higher ups from ‘The inside’ decided that it’s people were getting too familiar with the humans on “The Other Side”.
